<p class="p0">《Grotesk 的过去与未来：Aktiv Grotesk 批评》<a href="http://www.typeisbeautiful.com/2010/09/2935/">http://www.typeisbeautiful.com/2010/09/2935/</a></p>
<p class="p0">《拉丁字體的歷史：過渡時期字體》 <a href="http://blog.justfont.com/2012/11/%E6%8B%89%E4%B8%81%E5%AD%97%E9%AB%94%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%EF%BC%9A%E9%81%8E%E6%B8%A1%E6%99%82%E6%9C%9F%E5%AD%97%E9%AB%94/">http://blog.justfont.com/2012/11/%E6%8B%89%E4%B8%81%E5%AD%97%E9%AB%94%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%EF%BC%9A%E9%81%8E%E6%B8%A1%E6%99%82%E6%9C%9F%E5%AD%97%E9%AB%94/</a></p>
<p class="p0">《最时尚的英文字体：现代样式》</p>
<p class="p0"><a href="http://blog.justfont.com/2012/12/%E6%9C%80%E6%99%82%E5%B0%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E9%AB%94%EF%BC%9A%E7%8F%BE%E4%BB%A3%E6%A8%A3%E5%BC%8F/">http://blog.justfont.com/2012/12/%E6%9C%80%E6%99%82%E5%B0%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E9%AB%94%EF%BC%9A%E7%8F%BE%E4%BB%A3%E6%A8%A3%E5%BC%8F/</a></p>
<p>(本文出自腾讯CDC博客: <a href="http://cdc.tencent.com/?p=8565" target="_blank">http://cdc.tencent.com/?p=8565</a>)</p>";s:14:"date_timestamp";i:1437384835;}i:2;a:14:{s:5:"title";s:24:"互联网CEO大会总结";s:4:"link";s:30:"http://cdc.tencent.com/?p=8435";s:8:"comments";s:39:"http://cdc.tencent.com/?p=8435#comments";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Mon, 29 Jun 2015 08:16:09 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:5:"CDCer";}s:8:"category";s:12:"视觉设计";s:4:"guid";s:30:"http://cdc.tencent.com/?p=8435";s:11:"description";s:381:"<p><a href="http://cdc.tencent.com/?p=8435" target="_blank"><img src="http://cdc.tencent.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/banner1.jpg"/></a></p>互联网CEO分享会 - 互联网CEO们分享、交流、学习的平台
